         <abstract>
            <p>A letter (<foreign xml:lang="la">prosphoneticus</foreign> ) by <persName
                  ref="PRS3255CyrilI"/> addressed to Princesses Arcadia and Marina, sisters of
                  <persName ref="PRS9480Theodosi"/>. The letter, originally composed in Greek
               according to <bibl type="CPG">
                  <ptr target="bm:CPG3"/>
               </bibl>discusses the nature of Christ, aiming to limit the influence of <persName
                  ref="PRS7553Nestoriu"/>. Its Geez version is known as part of <title
                  ref="LIT3309Qerellos"> collection.</title>
            </p>
         </abstract>
